messages.zh: 第五关（后）
messages.tl: Fifth level (post)
babble--!

messages.zh: 快找掩体！
messages.tl: Find a bunker!

messages.zh: 我没事，只是擦伤而已，不要紧......
messages.tl: I am fine, just scratching, it doesn't matter...

messages.zh: 刚才帮助我们的......是谁？
messages.tl: Who helped us... who is it?

messages.zh: 路过的感染者......吗？
messages.tl: Passing Infected Person...?

messages.zh: 不管是谁，都成功帮我们争取到了时间！
messages.tl: No matter who it is, it has succeeded in helping us win the time!

messages.zh: 还不够......再这样下去，包围圈会不断紧缩。
messages.tl: Not enough... If you go on like this, the encirclement will continue to tighten.

messages.zh: {@nickname}博士已经发现了突破口，但没有增援，我们只能采取守势，无法突围......！
messages.tl: Dr. PLAYER has discovered a breakthrough, but there is no reinforcement. We can only take a defensive and cannot break through...!

messages.zh: ......再坚持一下！优先火力压制对方射手！我们来处理先锋！
messages.tl: ... stick to it! Priority firepower suppresses the other shooter! Let's deal with the pioneer!

messages.zh: 没错，没错！再多挣扎一点！再让我多看一看你们挣扎的样子！
messages.tl: That's right, that's right! Struggle a little more! Let me see more of your struggles!

messages.zh: 然后就去死吧，像雨夜中的火星一样！
messages.tl: Then go to hell, like Mars in the rainy night!

messages.zh: 还没完——还没完——！
messages.tl: Not finished yet - not finished yet!

messages.zh: 偶数干员退列休息！后备干员各自填补位置！不要让整合运动打开哪怕一丁点缺口！
messages.tl: Even-numbered staff retired to rest! The reserve cadres each fill the position! Don't let the Reunion Movement open even a little bit of a gap!

messages.zh: 如果必要的话——
messages.tl: If necessary -

messages.zh: 什么？什——不唔唔唔唔唔啊啊啊！！！
messages.tl: what? What? No, no, ah! ! !

messages.zh: 唔唔？撞飞起来了？发生什么了——
messages.tl: Hey? Hit it up? what happened--
This...what...

messages.zh: 你们比我预期的慢上太多。我可是连平民都顺手安顿好了。
messages.tl: You are too slower than I expected. I have settled down even the civilians.

messages.zh: 迅速打开通路，别给敌人重整阵形的机会！
messages.tl: Open the passage quickly, don't give the enemy a chance to reshape the formation!

messages.zh: 临光小姐！！
messages.tl: Miss Nearl! !

messages.zh: 我在。阿米娅你没事就好。
messages.tl: I'm here. Amiya, you are fine.

messages.zh: 幸亏这次作战有你参加。
messages.tl: Fortunately, this battle has you participated.

messages.zh: 信号定位很有效。看来你们遇到的麻烦确实不小。
messages.tl: Signal positioning is very effective. It seems that the trouble you have encountered is not small.

messages.zh: 您就是{@nickname}博士吧？
messages.tl: Are you Dr. PLAYER?

messages.zh: 耀骑士临光，前来迎接你们了。
messages.tl: Yao Knight, come to greet you.
